1. Make divisions (ie, nonreduced fractions) partitionable.

2. Rename ratio selector 'index' keyword to 'item'.
   Also rename ...
        selectortools.SingleContextCounttimeComponentSelector
        selectortools.SingleContextCounttimeComponentSliceSelector
   ... to ...
        selectortools.SingleContextCounttimeComponentItemSelector
        selectortools.SingleContextCounttimeComponentSliceSelector
   ... to cause naming parallelism between the two selector types.

3. Extend all selector classes with read-only 'context_name' property (string).
   Extend all selector classes with read-only 'context_names' property (list).  

4. Rename Selector.context to Selector.context_name. 
   Rename Selector.contexts to Selector.context_names.
